==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Cobelligerent
<hw>Co`bel*lig"er*ent</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A nation or state that
carries on war in connection with another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

